media:group.media:title: Transfer Learning with TensorFlow
media:group.media:description:
I'll livestream code and explain everything you could want to know about Transfer Learning using TensorFlow. 

Transfer learning occurs when you take a model trained to perform a certain task and reuse it to perform another task. Often enormous resources are required to train a model to do a sophisticated task. If you can find a model that was trained on a related task you can cut your development time.

In this video I'll cover all of the following Live : 

✳️ Transfer Learning
✳️ TensorFlow Hub
✳️ Multi-Class Convolutional Neural Networks
✳️ Downloading & Processing Data
✳️ Activation
✳️ Pooling
✳️ Optimizing Performance
✳️ Minimizing Overfitting
✳️ Augmenting Images
✳️ ResNet
✳️ EfficientNet
✳️ Much More!
